<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870518-0040 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:Mcdonald's Corp.</HL><DD> 05/18/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> MCDDIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><TEXT>   MCDONALD'S CORP. said it approved a 3-for-2 stock split and a 14% increase in its quarterly cash dividend. The split is payable June 22 to stock of record June 8. The increased dividend of 18.75 cents a share, or 12.5 cents a share on a post-split basis, is payable June 5 to shares of record May 27. The previous dividend was 16.5 cents a share, or 11 cents on a post-split basis. The fast-food concern is based in Oak Brook, Ill. </TEXT></DOC>